data.description: This Penthouse was made for entertaining & designed to wow! From the moment you walk into the foyer you will know you have stepped into elegant living. The fully custom kitchen has dark knotted wood cabinets from floor to ceiling combined with a rare, natural edge, Fusion Red Quartzite counter and backsplash.A walk in pantry, Slate and Stainless appliances & a beautiful range hood this kitchen is not only functional, but a gorgeous show stopper! The open floor concept with soaring 16 ft ceilings makes for a grandeur, main living space. Tile and Luxury Vinyl planks cover the floors & 4 sets of French doors lead you out to the open air balcony that oversees the pool and faces East, perfect for entertaining friends and family, or waking up with a cup of coffee and watching the sunrise. Relax in the master suite beside the fireplace or soak in the large tub. Bella Harbor truly offers stress-free living, as everything is taken care of for you, including the Spanish tile roof, everything exterior, the community pool, pest control, garbage pickup, landscaping and maintenance, plumbing, and drywall. Ideally located, Bella Harbor is less than half a mile from the Palm Coast Marina, and only a mile away from the Hammock Beach, and Jungle Hut beach. This luxurious condo is also zoned for the highest rated schools in Flagler County. Come grab your own piece of paradise before it is gone.
